OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FMore than 14 million motorists will
OL,7,Fembark on their holidays on Friday at
OL,8,Fa time when the EU's new Entry/Exit
OL,9,FSystem (EES) is causing huge delays
OL,10,Ffor people hoping to enter the
OL,11,FSchengen Area.
OL,13,FThe estimate from the RAC has led to
OL,14,Fdire warnings of delays, with people
OL,15,Fbeing urged to plan for significant
OL,16,Fwait times.
OL,18,FDover is expected to be the most
OL,19,Fheavily impacted, and experts say
OL,20,Fdrivers hoping to travel to France
OL,21,Fcould face Brexit-like delays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
