PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784009885
OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FIn preparation for the uptick in
OL,7,Ftravellers, France announced over the
OL,8,Fweekend it would be deploying more
OL,9,Fborder guards on British soil to cope
OL,10,Fwith the new paperwork.
OL,12,FThe concerns over border delays are
OL,13,Frelated to the EU's new EES checks.
OL,15,FThe system, rolled out fully in April,
OL,16,Finvolves people from third-party
OL,17,Fcountries such as the UK having their
OL,18,Ffingerprints registered and
OL,19,Fphotographs taken to enter the
OL,20,FSchengen Area, which consists of 29
OL,21,FEuropean countries, mainly in the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
