FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784009885
OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FFor most UK travellers, the process is
OL,7,Fdone at foreign airports, but it is
OL,8,Falso carried out at the Port of Dover,
OL,9,FEurotunnel's Folkestone terminal and
OL,10,FLondon St Pancras railway station.
OL,12,FMany passengers have spent hours stuck
OL,13,Fin EES queues in recent months.
OL,15,FIt is supposed to be easier to enter
OL,16,Fthe bloc once the initial scan has
OL,17,Fbeen done, but many border points are
OL,18,Freportedly collecting the same initial
OL,19,Fscans multiple times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
