PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784009885
OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fbrokered the agreement for the
OL,8,Fincreased presence with her French
OL,9,Fcounterpart, Philippe Tabarot, ahead
OL,10,Fof the summer holidays.
OL,12,FThis extra presence will be in place
OL,13,Fwhile the French border force awaits
OL,14,Fthe installation of new passport
OL,15,Fbooths and tablets.
OL,17,FMinisters have announced they will
OL,18,Fprovide #20 million of funding to
OL,19,Fincrease the number of booths, on top
OL,20,Fof #10.5m they have already put
OL,21,Ftowards preventing disruption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
