OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FThe RAC said the number of journeys
OL,7,Fexpected this weekend is the second
OL,8,Fhighest since it started tracking data
OL,9,Fin 2022, surpassed only by 18.8
OL,10,Fmillion in 2022 when the easing of
OL,11,Fcoronavirus restrictions sparked a
OL,12,Fsurge in travel.
OL,14,FMost schools in England and Wales
OL,15,Fbreak up for the summer holidays at
OL,16,Fthe end of this week or early next
OL,17,Fweek, while the academic year has
OL,18,Falready ended in Scotland and Northern
OL,19,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
