OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784009885
OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FThe RAC predicted that Saturday will
OL,7,Fbe the busiest day on the roads for
OL,8,Fgetaway journeys, with 3.8 million
OL,9,Fplanned.
OL,11,FFriday and Sunday will each see an
OL,12,Festimated 3.4 million journeys. A
OL,13,Ffurther 6.8 million trips will be
OL,14,Ftaken, spread across the three days,
OL,15,Fwith drivers unsure which exact day
OL,16,Fthey will hit the road.
OL,18,FThe RAC warned that south-west and
OL,19,Fnorth-west England are likely to see
OL,20,Fthe most leisure traffic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
