OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FDrivers embarking on getaway road
OL,7,Fjourneys will be hit by fuel prices
OL,8,Fbeing much higher than a year ago.
OL,10,FFilling a 55-litre family car costs an
OL,11,Fadditional #8.90 for petrol and #21.20
OL,12,Ffor diesel, based on average prices.
OL,14,FHow can people prepare for the delays?
OL,16,FRAC breakdown spokesperson Harriet
OL,17,FHernando warned people to be ready for
OL,18,Fthe summer traffic jams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
