OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FShe said: "People should prepare for
OL,7,Fdelays and getting stuck in a jam in
OL,8,Fpotentially very hot weather; people
OL,9,Fshould carry plenty of water, as well
OL,10,Fas suncream and an umbrella to provide
OL,11,Fshade."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FCars without air conditioning could be
OL,19,Fparticularly vulnerable with the
OL,20,Fheatwave expected to last until the
OL,21,Fweekend.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@GO]
