OL,3,CHuge traffic jams expected at Dover as
OL,4,CEU Entry/Exit System causes delays
OL,6,FIn Dover, the current forecast for the
OL,7,Fweekend ranges from 21C to 25C.
OL,9,FLeaving earlier or later in the day,
OL,10,Fif possible, to avoid the worst of the
OL,11,Fsun might be a good option.
OL,13,FIf you're getting a ferry, then do not
OL,14,Ffret about the traffic causing you to
OL,15,Fmiss it. If you're unable to get on
OL,16,Fyour scheduled ferry, most ferry
OL,17,Ftickets offer flexible boarding, and
OL,18,Fthe operators will usually find you a
OL,19,Fspot on the next one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
